      w3a sylbi syl2anc eqeltrd wss uzss 3sstr4g sselda syldan cshi oveq2 nn0ex
      cc zcn mptex shftval syl2an 3eqtr4rd seqfeq seqshft seqeq1d oveq1d 3eqtrd
      subid c1 cdiv recnd clt max2 sylancl absid lt01 ifboth eqbrtrd geolim cvv
      breq1 wb seqex climshft syl3anc mpbird breldm wral ralrimiva fveq2 eleq1d
      a1i rcla4v sylc abscl cmul fveq2d breq12d imbi2d leid exp0 eqtrd breqtrrd
      wi mulid1 remulcl lemul2a ex syl112anc mul12 eleq2s ax-1cn addsub syl2anr
      expp1 mp3an2 mulcom breq2d sylibd peano2uzs sylan2 cbvralv sylib jca max1
      absge0 lemul1a syl31anc letrd peano2uz letr syld expcom a2d uzind4 impcom
